{"tid":644872,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"感性摩佬：後悔與雲加衝突","createTime":"2018-04-27T14:44:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-27T16:40:47.000Z","uid":46892,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"8afd97421a0f2ed6bdc15f13869fe15a5816623c","tid":644872,"uid":46892,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T14:44:12.000Z","msg":"【<a href=\"http://now.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnow.com&d=0dcvmh6q41fXOr6Ir49lS0%2FDJpISyAq9ELy6OyFxwDc%3D&h=bc9626e5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">now.com</a>體育】周日曼聯大戰阿仙奴，有可能是兩大宿敵摩連奴與雲加最後一次在英超舞台正面交鋒，既可能是最後一次，摩佬也難禁感性一番。<br />\n<br />\n摩連奴於2004年登陸英超，很快就與阿仙奴的雲加鬥個正著，由場內鬥到場外，多年對戰不乏經典場面及口水戰，其中摩佬就曾稱雲加為「失敗專家」。被問到可有後悔與雲加心存敵意時，摩連奴在賽前記者會上說：「有些事情沒有就更好，一些動作、一些言語，現在沒有了，我感覺較好。」<br />\n<br />\n「不過在2004年，阿仙奴是著名的『全季不敗』。之後數年與他們拉鋸，對方是令人驚奇的球隊，把我們推向極限，在高貝利的對賽令人難忘。大戰，激鬥，衷心感謝。後悔？一些負面的事，是的，也許他也一樣。」摩佬說時顯得感慨。<br />\n<br />\n此外，摩佬又被問及門將迪基亞可會在今夏離隊，他答得斬釘截鐵：「沒有機會。」"},{"pid":"0b1596913d8901b55cdce70f3e8674c18dd385b5","tid":644872,"uid":22589,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T14:51:21.000Z","msg":"同雲加作對的人 上天會看到"},{"pid":"efbaceac92cf65285708023f5b34b351fd31fe09","tid":644872,"uid":5549,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T16:27:22.000Z","msg":"貓哭老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0a6c26556d5a96ec11efed1789c244b580c062a9","tid":644872,"uid":33730,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"efbaceac92cf65285708023f5b34b351fd31fe09","tid":644872,"uid":5549,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T16:27:22.000Z","msg":"貓哭老鼠<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-27T16:30:39.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/05/08/091008_5f51359d107579c976ffc56964e09e10.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F05%2F08%2F091008_5f51359d107579c9